- Or worse,you do the same thing to somebody else.

508
00:31:14,550 --> 00:31:16,580
Even your own kid.
No.
That's not me.

509
00:31:16,580 --> 00:31:19,260
John,we need your help here.

510
00:31:19,260 --> 00:31:22,130
We know what mr.Hathaway liked.

511
00:31:22,560 --> 00:31:24,930
- What he did to you...
- the photos he took of you.

512
00:31:24,930 --> 00:31:26,350
What-what photos?

513
00:31:26,350 --> 00:31:30,080
The ones of you in bed,sleeping with your thumb in your mouth.

514
00:31:30,080 --> 00:31:33,570
Posed just like his son clay after he killed him.

515
00:31:35,100 --> 00:31:37,790
- It's okay,you can tell us.
- No,it's not okay!

516
00:31:37,790 --> 00:31:40,820
All right it never was.
And I don't care what you think.

517
00:31:40,820 --> 00:31:44,040
It wasn't mr.
Hathaway who took the photos.

518
00:32:38,950 --> 00:32:41,120
go to sleep,son.

519
00:32:46,360 --> 00:32:48,940
Night,daddy.

520
00:32:57,140 --> 00:33:00,030
It was your father who took those pictures?

521
00:33:01,300 --> 00:33:04,050
I swear my father never touched me in that way.

522
00:33:05,080 --> 00:33:07,860
Maybe because you were his own son.

523
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:12,360
You were off-limits.

524
00:33:13,540 --> 00:33:16,340
But clay wasn't so lucky.

525
00:33:25,910 --> 00:33:27,820
yeah?
Rush.

526
00:33:29,870 --> 00:33:32,560
