- I need a marked car to go to 8th and walnut.

527
00:33:32,570 --> 00:33:35,420
- Okay,cliff burrell.
Just send the car over and meet me there.
- Right now?
Where?

528
00:33:35,420 --> 00:33:37,260
What do you mean?
Why not?

529
00:33:37,260 --> 00:33:38,650
- Hang up.
- What?

530
00:33:38,650 --> 00:33:40,510
Hang up.

531
00:33:40,820 --> 00:33:43,960
Hathaway just took cliff burrell up to the roof of the building
where he works.

532
00:33:44,130 --> 00:33:44,630
What?

533
00:33:44,630 --> 00:33:46,630
- Boss said swat is en route.
- That ain't possible.

534
00:33:46,630 --> 00:33:50,010
How the hell could hathaway have known it was burrell?

535
00:33:52,230 --> 00:33:53,920
Scotty?

536
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:56,650
I told him about the pictures tara found.

537
00:33:56,650 --> 00:33:58,710
I thought it was him.

538
00:33:58,710 --> 00:34:00,770
We got to go.

539
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:29,790
Go to the edge.
Go to the edge.
Please,please.

540
00:34:29,790 --> 00:34:31,800
Move!

541
00:34:34,930 --> 00:34:36,220
move!

542
00:34:37,550 --> 00:34:39,100
shut up!

543
00:34:41,710 --> 00:34:43,180
shut up!

544
00:34:46,210 --> 00:34:47,970
shut up!

545
00:34:58,440 --> 00:34:59,970
mitch!

546
00:35:03,300 --> 00:35:05,240
Mitch,it's me.

547
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:10,330
- It's me,detective valens.
- That's fine right there,detective.

548
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:12,420
I know it wasn't you,mitch.

549
00:35:12,420 --> 00:35:14,370
I'm on your side here.

550
00:35:15,340 --> 00:35:18,660
I gave up believing anybody was on my side a long time ago.

551
00:35:18,660 --> 00:35:21,230
Understood,but listen to me now.

552
00:35:22,470 --> 00:35:24,490
You don't put down that gun and step back,

553
00:35:24,490 --> 00:35:27,060
these guys are going to put a bullet in your brain.

554
00:35:27,060 --> 00:35:29,800
I don't plan on walking off this roof alive.

555
00:35:29,810 --> 00:35:31,900
But I'm taking this piece of garbage with me.

556
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:33,080
- Please,please!
- Shut up!

557
00:35:33,080 --> 00:35:35,580
I know you want to kill him,mitch.
I understand,I do,but...

558
00:35:35,580 --> 00:35:38,310
you don't want to die this way.

559
00:35:40,090 --> 00:35:42,720
he killed my son.

560
00:35:43,260 --> 00:35:46,750
He planted those photos,he turned my wife against me.

561
00:35:47,620 --> 00:35:48,830
Mitch...

562
00:35:48,830 --> 00:35:51,140
tell him what you did.

563
00:35:51,140 --> 00:35:53,380
I want to know before you die.
Tell him what you did.

564
00:35:53,380 --> 00:35:55,140
Tell him!
Tell him damn it!

565
00:35:55,140 --> 00:35:57,050
Mitch,this won't bring your son back.

566
00:35:57,050 --> 00:35:59,710
Oh,you're going to die,you're going to die.
You're going to die...

567
00:35:59,710 --> 00:36:01,270
Stop!
Mitch!

568
00:36:01,270 --> 00:36:02,750
No!

569
00:36:02,750 --> 00:36:04,150
Stop!

570
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:06,160
- Stop!
- Easy,mitch!

571
00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:08,130
Tara.

572
00:36:11,380 --> 00:36:13,370
he did this.

573
00:36:13,460 --> 00:36:15,240
To clay.

574
00:36:16,130 --> 00:36:17,830
To us.

575
00:36:18,900 --> 00:36:21,180
I'm sorry,mitch.

576
00:36:22,390 --> 00:36:25,500
I'm so sorry I didn't believe you.

577
00:36:26,350 --> 00:36:28,810
I let you down.

578
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:32,630
But I lost him.

579
00:36:34,010 --> 00:36:36,410
I looked away.

580
00:36:37,750 --> 00:36:40,060
I never should have looked away.

581
00:36:40,060 --> 00:36:42,980
No,this is not your fault,mitch.

582
00:36:45,660 --> 00:36:48,120
Don't do this,mitch.

583
00:36:49,150 --> 00:36:51,620
Oh,please,

584
00:36:51,620 --> 00:36:54,590
don't do this.

585
00:36:54,720 --> 00:36:57,240
I need you.

586
00:37:00,230 --> 00:37:02,840
Do you know I never stopped loving you?

587
00:37:03,330 --> 00:37:05,380
Me,too.

588
00:37:05,820 --> 00:37:07,790
Me,too.

589
00:37:09,430 --> 00:37:11,100
Cliff,just...

590
00:37:11,580 --> 00:37:13,600
tell the truth.

591
00:37:13,600 --> 00:37:16,580
We know how you watched his son while he slept,took pictures of
him.

592
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:20,750
I...
I'm so sorry...

593
00:37:20,950 --> 00:37:24,150
but you couldn't touch johnny,'cause he was yours.

594
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:26,450
I swore I never would.

595
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:28,890
So you took mine.

596
00:37:31,090 --> 00:37:33,740
You took my boy from me.

597
00:37:36,170 --> 00:37:38,030
I fought it for...

598
00:37:38,060 --> 00:37:39,800
for so long.

599
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,640
The feelings.

600
00:37:41,640 --> 00:37:43,100
And then,I-I...

601
00:37:43,100 --> 00:37:44,640
I couldn't anymore.

602
00:37:44,640 --> 00:37:46,720
I'm so sorry.

603
00:37:59,260 --> 00:38:01,980
Hey,little buddy,what happened?

604
00:38:01,980 --> 00:38:03,610
Damon took my bike.

605
00:38:03,610 --> 00:38:07,260
He pushed me off,and I scraped up my knee.

606
00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:12,800
- Tore it up pretty good,huh?
- It hurts bad.

607
00:38:12,980 --> 00:38:15,130
Well,let me seeee.

608
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:21,870
Yeah.

609
00:38:23,550 --> 00:38:26,740
Need to clean that up,get you a bandage.

610
00:38:27,930 --> 00:38:30,530
I'll just walk home.

611
00:38:30,690 --> 00:38:31,970
It's okay.

612
00:38:31,970 --> 00:38:34,010
I got a first aid kit in my tool chest.

613
00:38:34,010 --> 00:38:36,020
Something to take the sting out.

614
00:38:36,020 --> 00:38:37,860
I don't know.

615
00:38:39,060 --> 00:38:41,240
Won't hurt a bit,promise.

616
00:38:41,830 --> 00:38:44,910
My dad always tells me just walk it off.

617
00:38:45,810 --> 00:38:47,260
Come on.

618
00:38:47,260 --> 00:38:49,260
You're bleeding.

619
00:38:50,200 --> 00:38:53,920
You want a soda or something?
Got a fridge full back in the garage.

